Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手指粗短 老二像小蘑菇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stubby fingers, little mushroom cock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到他的名字了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I heard his name,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时瓦利德在为他鼓劲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when Walid was cheering him on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定鲁祖向瓦利德承诺 给他萨嘎尔瓦达贫民窟土地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you're sure Rujul promised Walid the Sagar Wada slum land?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是他们的助兴节目 帮助他们完成交易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were their entertainment, a way for them to seal their deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个女孩森妮很清楚情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The other girl, Sunny, understood it all,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是谁 他们在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who they were, what they were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁祖和瓦利德完全不在乎 我们听到了他们的对话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rujul and Walid didn't give a shit if we heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(居民楼)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后森妮消失了 周不放我走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then Sunny disappeared, and Zhou wouldn't let me leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不贿赂那个女仆来给你送信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Had to bribe that maid to come tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她死了 对吧 森妮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's dead, isn't she? Sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是认识你 我也一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd be the same if I didn't know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都死死地盯着我 我以为他们一定很恨我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They all stared at me with such intensity, that I thought they must hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我明白了 他们不过是在看着我的恐惧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now I know they were simply staring at my fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人们感到恐惧的是他们对自己的了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's what people know about themselves that makes them afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 厕所在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me. Where's the toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨晚怎么又喊又叫的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much shouting and yelling you were doing last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做噩梦了 所以我今早没叫醒你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bad dreams, na? That is why I let you sleep this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 听着 我真的得去...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Great. Listen, I really need to go to the--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 林 这是拉克什米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey! Lin, this is Lakshmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们昨晚吃的煎饼是她做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She made the roti we were eating last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 嗨 你好 谢谢你 很美味\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi. Hey. Thank you. Was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是萨嘎尔瓦达贫民区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the Sagar Wada jhopadpatti.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.91,0:14:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是贱民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are the not-people,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些棚屋是我们勉强度日的贱屋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and these hutments are the not-houses where we are not living.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是谁的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whose are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的丈夫 他不在了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her husband. He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:14:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能拿走她亡夫的鞋子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't take her dead husband's shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是死了 林先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not dead, Linbaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是去迪拜工作了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gone to Dubai only, for the work there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的需要大便 -我们走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I really do need to shit. -Let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合脚吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's good?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以喝吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你认为有帮助的话 喝吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you think it helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正还能坏到哪去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't make it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过你想戒酒的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said you want to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道如果你把鲁祖的事 告诉卡德尔拜 会有什么后果吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what'll happen if you tell Khaderbhai about Rujul, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以对此保持沉默\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We could stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果鲁祖要背叛我们 那我过去一年的辛苦都白费了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If Rujul's betraying us, then I've worked the last year for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原本会任我死在宫殿里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You would've let me rot in the Palace
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不知道威胁你宝贵地皮交易的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if I hadn't known something that threatened your precious land deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你利用了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You used me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和毛里齐奥 莫德纳有什么区别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you any different than Maurizio and Modena?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你才是利用人的那个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or maybe you're the one doing the using.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不在乎鲁祖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't give a shit about Rujul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒品 我 那两个男的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The drugs, me, those guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.19,0:16:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是让你找替罪羊 为自己推脱责任的方式罢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just a way to pass the buck and take no responsibility for yourself whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿润 你好吗 强尼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you doing, Arun? Johnny?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prabhu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去招待他们 -你不用去 我去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll help them. -You won't. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把桌子清理了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go clean the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要些什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩都要奶茶和煎饼 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chai and roti for us both, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 坐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come. Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐吧 南堤塔做的是 全孟买最美味的奶茶 相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sit, na. Nandita is making world best chai in all Bombay. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 阿姨 多谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Arre, thank you, Kaaki. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这白人是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who's the gora?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我新的生意合伙人 -生意合伙人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is my new business partner. -Business partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会一起合作旅游生意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are going to be working together in the tourist business.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕瓦蒂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Parvati?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对她说了什么  -说你是我的好友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you say to her? -That you are my good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是帕瓦蒂 我一定会娶她 林先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is Parvati, and I am determined to marry her, Linbaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的女友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没说她是我的女友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did not say she was my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们第一次说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the first time we've ever spoken words to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前从没和她说过话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've never spoken to her before?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是里程碑式的一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is a momentous day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴我在场见证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, glad I could be here to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 哥们 我得弄清自己的处境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen, mate. I need to figure out my situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能去找官方机构\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't go to your authorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.13,0:18:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴... -但你需要钱 对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shut the fuck-- -But you are needing money, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想怎么帮你快速弄到钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have been thinking to help you get it very fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火车票呢 去你村庄的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about the train tickets? To your village.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在吧 能转卖吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You still have them, right? Can we sell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难卖出火车已经驶出车站的票 不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very difficult to sell tickets for a train that has already left the station. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得最好的主意是成为生意合伙人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it is best idea to become business partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起当孟买导游\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To be Bombay guides together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉布 我不会留在这里 -林先生 你想想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not staying, Prabhu. -Just think, Linbaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会赚大钱 -我只需要找到卡拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So much money will be coming. -I just need to get to Karla.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请听我说 我们俩都可以... -我不行 帕拉布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen to me, please. We could both be-- -I can't, Prabhu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚非常感谢 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for last night. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你救了我的命 真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were a lifesaver. You really were.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不会留在这里谋生计 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I'm not staying here and hustling, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不可能的 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just not gonna happen. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.22,0:19:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我之后会回来拿我的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. I'll be back for my stuff later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉 是林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Karla, it's Lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉 你在吗 我得和你聊聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Karla, you there? I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了  -周夫人知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened? -Madame Zhou figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们差点杀死我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They almost killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们抢了我的钱 护照 一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They took my money, my passport, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我警告过你这事很危险 -的确 现在我完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I warned you it was dangerous. -You did, yeah. Now I'm fucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去找你的大使馆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then go to your embassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和我有什么关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How is that my problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:19:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉 我不懂你为什么这个样子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Karla, I don't understand why you're being like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来寻求帮助的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm asking for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉 你得帮帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Karla, you need to fucking help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有责任做任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't need to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have somewhere to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她当真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is she for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看上去需要喝一杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You look like a man who needs a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道昨晚你没把所有毒品给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you didn't give me all the dope last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在由我说了算 不是她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now it's up to me, not her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉在几里外就能看出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Karla can spot them a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看出来什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁可以利用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}People she can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没有逼迫我做任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She didn't force me to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要逼迫 这是她的天赋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Didn't need to. It's her gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉到底有什么特别的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's so special about Karla anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.22,0:21:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和她一样漂亮啊 不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm as beautiful as she is, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我摸上去的感觉比看上去还要好呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel even better than I look.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莎 你不需要这样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lisa, you don't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我想爽一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe I wanna feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢 我们可以一起爽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't you? We can feel good together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嗑嗨了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're shit-faced.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么男人都喜欢贱人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why do men like bitches?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人就喜欢对自己不好的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They fall over women who treat them like shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法自拔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't get enough of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太糟糕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This fucking sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.65,0:21:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前没试过戒毒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You never tried to quit before?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢嗑嗨的感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like being high.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢与现实拉开一点距离\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like there being some distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.28,0:22:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于现实生活的事 我不擅长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not good with life stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.08,0:22:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未擅长过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.42,0:22:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许卡拉把这个留下 是因为她知道你会找到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe Karla left that 'cause she knew you'd find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.46,0:22:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼 你说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.96,0:22:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我磕了这个 她就可以赶我走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I take this, she can throw me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.47,0:22:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不像外表看上去那么没脑子 林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not as dumb as you look, Lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吐了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna puke.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉要维持多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long is it this bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.91,0:22:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.45,0:22:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后会好转吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then it gets better?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.79,0:22:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.30,0:23:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会想念吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't miss it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.01,0:23:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡德尔拜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Khaderbhai.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.18,0:23:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿和平与你同在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salaam alaikum. Alaikumu assalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.06,0:23:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到你很高兴 请坐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's good to see you. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.35,0:23:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.98,0:24:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切可好 你说情况紧急\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is everything all right? You said it was urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.32,0:24:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨晚去了宫殿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I went to the Palace last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.65,0:24:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不放下执着 你对周的憎恨将永远不会消失\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your hate for Zhou is a wound that will never heal if you keep picking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.70,0:24:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周扣押了我的朋友莉莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Zhou was holding my friend Lisa prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.24,0:24:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为莉莎知道的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because of what Lisa knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.25,0:24:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人背叛我们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're being betrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.88,0:24:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们合作的领域 一直以来是孟买的日常生意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our business together has been the usual Bombay dhanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.72,0:24:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贿赂和协定 大家都知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bribes and understandings, what everyone expects.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.10,0:24:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我有别的生意 你很清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I have other business. You know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.52,0:24:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出于对你的尊重和喜爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Out of respect and affection for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.31,0:24:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从未要求你跨越 我两个世界的界线 卡拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've never asked you to cross the line between my two worlds, Karla.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.53,0:24:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定吗  -如果不肯定 我不会来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you certain? -I wouldn't be here if I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.86,0:24:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须肯定自己准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, you must be certain that you are ready
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.45,0:24:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受把这次背叛告诉我的后果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for what telling me about this betrayal means.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.95,0:25:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不把我所知道的告诉你 你会蒙受重创\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I don't tell you what I know, then you'll suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.33,0:25:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反 你愿意为我蒙受重创\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Instead, you would suffer for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.84,0:25:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为我做了那么多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've done so much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.63,0:25:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们之间不存在谁欠谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is no debt between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.17,0:25:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱不计较得失 砝码或交换\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Love has no accounting or ledger or quid pro quo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.26,0:25:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们投入爱里 是因为无论是否有回报 我们的内心坚持如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We invest it because our heart insists without any demand of return.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.14,0:25:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉 这是你仍需要学习的最重要一课\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this is the lesson, above all others, you still need to learn, Karla.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.95,0:25:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁祖阿德卡在和瓦利德沙私会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rujul Aadekar has been meeting with Walid Shah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.24,0:25:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会接受瓦利德对萨嘎尔瓦达的投标 而不是我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He will accept Walid's bid for Sagar Wada, not ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.88,0:25:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事你最好没搞错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You better not be wrong about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.74,0:26:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.46,0:26:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道人们为何不能更友善\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know why people can't be nicer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.54,0:26:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为一个女孩吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was it a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.88,0:26:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你第一次尝试海洛因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Turned you on to heroin the first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.22,0:26:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.80,0:26:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.43,0:26:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们坠入黑洞的永远是爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's always love that sends us down the rabbit hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.90,0:26:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.20,0:26:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我信任你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.12,0:27:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我们有钱去印度 我们可以每天这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once we have the money to go to India, we can do this every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.63,0:27:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定会玩得爽翻 宝贝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're gonna have such an amazing time, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.52,0:27:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我个忙好吗 丢了那玩意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do me a favor? Get rid of that shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.61,0:27:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.36,0:27:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莎 嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lisa. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.99,0:27:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁祖阿德卡是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who's Rujul Aadekar?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.79,0:27:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当你没听见过吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forget you ever heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.21,0:27:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.50,0:27:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 忘了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Leave that alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.50,0:27:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在帮我 我也要帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're helping me. I'm helping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.98,0:28:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫殿之所以能存在 是因为它从来都不选边站\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Palace is allowed to exist because it has never taken sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.23,0:28:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将提醒周 她经营生意所依靠的宽宏大量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Zhou will be reminded of the grace under which she operates.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.49,0:28:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我说说这个帮了你的男人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me about this man who helped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.74,0:28:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫林福特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His name is Lin Ford.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.78,0:28:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他即将离开 所以我利用他把莉莎弄出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew he was about to leave town, so I used him to get Lisa out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.87,0:28:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是信任他 对你来说这不是个简单的举动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must have trusted him. That is no small thing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.42,0:28:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时很赶时间 他很合适\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was in a hurry. He fit the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.09,0:28:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道鲁祖的事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does he know about Rujul?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.88,0:28:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他听到名字了 别的没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He heard the name. Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.01,0:28:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道其中的意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Has no idea what any of it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.68,0:28:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一个聪明又有门路的人 也许会四处打听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But a smart and resourceful man might decide to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.89,0:28:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(雷纳尔多咖啡馆)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.06,0:28:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的...回头见 谢谢...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, okay. I'll see you soon. Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.98,0:28:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很荣幸...就像这样 对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pleasure. Pleasure. And we do it like this, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.32,0:28:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.24,0:29:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脸怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.90,0:29:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被打劫了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got mugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.45,0:29:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天 -我需要新的证件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wow. -I need new papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.33,0:29:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么问我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.16,0:29:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是我在孟买所认识最厉害的骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause you are the biggest crook I know in Bombay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.62,0:29:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无意冒犯 -完全不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No offense. -None taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.04,0:29:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜 原因不用和我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I can assume, for reasons I need not know,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.50,0:29:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能去找领事馆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that your consulate is not an option?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.92,0:29:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 否则你不会来找骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bien s?r. Or you wouldn't need a crook.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.76,0:29:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得买一本护照 你说你认识那个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to buy a passport. You said you know the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.01,0:29:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿布戴尔卡达尔可汗 掌控着孟买的假文件生意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Abdel Khader Khan controls the book business in Bombay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.06,0:29:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能安排我见他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, can you set me up with him?
