Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.52,0:29:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林 你读过《教父》吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you read The Godfather, Lin?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.86,0:29:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看过电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've seen the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.53,0:29:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是卡达尔可汗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is Khader Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.95,0:29:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是可以随随便便安排见面的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is not a man with whom you just get set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.53,0:29:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能给他什么 你说你没钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What would you offer him? You said you have no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.53,0:29:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一本有用的护照要价是一千美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A good passport, one worth having, will cost a thousand dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.70,0:29:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一千美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A thousand dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.54,0:29:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 我一定能做些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. There must be something I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.21,0:29:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人比你更了解这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one knows this place like you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.17,0:30:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为我们是朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought we were friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.96,0:30:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有朋友 这种时候就是原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do not have friends. Times like this are exactly why.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.34,0:30:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须做些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I gotta do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.68,0:30:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 我昨晚是在贫民窟过夜的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I slept in a fucking slum last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.85,0:30:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孟买一半的人都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As did half of Bombay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.31,0:30:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识一个叫鲁祖阿德卡的人吗  或是阿第克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know a guy called Rujul Aadekar? Or Ah-dee-kuhr.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.53,0:30:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 他是本地政客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, he's a local politician.
