Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.66,0:30:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...不要声...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just-- Keep your--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.83,0:30:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许这条消息会对某些人有价值\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe that information would be worth something to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.08,0:30:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能四处问问吗  -压低声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could you just ask around? -Keep your voice down.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.29,0:30:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去他的 我需要找回自由 迪迪埃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck that. I want my freedom back, Didier.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.54,0:30:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎是否会把周 卡拉她们拉下水 -你能冷静点吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't care if I screw over Zhou, Karla... -Will you calm down?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.67,0:30:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有教父 鲁祖 都无所谓 直到我如愿 无论...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...the Godfather, Rujul, whoever the fuck, until I get it. Whatev--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.17,0:30:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 -先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck. -Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.51,0:30:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《肮脏的哈里》 林 我看了录像版本的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dirty Harry, Lin. I've seen it now on VCR.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.64,0:30:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是西部片 但还是很不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not a Western, but very good all the same.
