Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.86,0:31:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很酷 -祝你好运 林 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's very cool. -Bonne chance, Lin. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.57,0:31:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你心想事成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wish you good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.24,0:31:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢《黄昏双镖客》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For a Few Dollars More is my favorite, yaar.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.87,0:31:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后可能是《西部执法者》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then maybe Josey Wales.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.70,0:31:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 不 我的前三名应该是 《镖客三部曲》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Actually, no, the whole Dollars trilogy would be my one-two-three.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.58,0:31:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后《西部执法者》是第四 因为...他演绎的方式实在是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then maybe Josey Wales is my fourth, because-- just the way he puts it all--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.46,0:31:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得聊聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You and me need to have a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.09,0:31:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是疯子 瞧瞧他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This guy is crazy. Look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.89,0:31:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我们摆脱他 抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me get rid of him. Apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.30,0:31:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想都别想 伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going nowhere, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.68,0:31:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚被人痛揍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just got the shit kicked out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.52,0:31:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我去帮卡拉把莉莎从宫殿里救出来之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After I went and helped Karla get Lisa out of the Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.73,0:31:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 莉莎怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? What happened to Lisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.40,0:31:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.15,0:31:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周扣押了她 她状态糟透了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Zhou was holding her prisoner. She's a fucking mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.36,0:31:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 你必须离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry. You need to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.66,0:31:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.66,0:31:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.49,0:31:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪 是个玩笑 你要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you going? It's a joke. Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.25,0:32:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你应该停止干涉我的生意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I think you should stop interfering with my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.17,0:32:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林 莉莎没事吧 她在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lin, is Lisa all right? Where is she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.34,0:32:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你以为我会告诉你们两个混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, you think I'd tell you arseholes?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.80,0:32:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周的手下抢走了我的钱和护照\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Zhou's people took my money and my passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.43,0:32:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来 这都是你们造成的 -嘿...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The way I see it, all of that is on you. -Hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.81,0:32:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是为了个毒虫妓女去搞英雄救美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you went to play hero for a junkie whore,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.65,0:32:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这是莉莎的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that is Lisa's problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.19,0:32:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是为了取悦卡拉 那是她的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you did it to please Karla... That is her problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.94,0:32:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你和我之间没有瓜葛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you and I, we have no relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.66,0:32:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不欠你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I owe you nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.49,0:32:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你说错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you're wrong about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.58,0:32:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想就这样离开 -哥们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't fucking walk away from me. -Arre, chaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.00,0:32:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 不 没关系 -别在这里闹 请坐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's okay. No, it's okay. -This is not the place. Please, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.67,0:32:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩都坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Both of you, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.83,0:32:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先 -请坐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After you. -Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.59,0:32:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为自己是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who the fuck do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.76,0:32:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然出现 把自己当成什么人物了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You turn up here, you think you matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.81,0:33:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 只有傻瓜才会 不摸清规则就玩游戏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, only a fool plays a game without knowing the rules first,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.15,0:33:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不了解其他玩家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or the other players.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.94,0:33:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫德纳 我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go, Modena.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.07,0:33:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想揍扁他那张笑着的俊脸蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to smash his pretty smiling face in.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.45,0:33:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我知道我可以 也因为那感觉一定很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I knew I could and because it would feel great.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.04,0:33:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但更多是因为我知道他是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But mainly 'cause I knew he was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.80,0:33:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prabhu.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.18,0:33:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 经过了今天上午 如果你让我滚 我不会怪你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, after this morning, I wouldn't blame you if you tell me to piss off,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.23,0:33:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我必须打个电话 而我没钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I need to make a phone call, and I've got no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.69,0:33:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.53,0:33:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.75,0:34:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能打国际长途吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I make an international call?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.67,0:34:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 林先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course, Linbaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.75,0:34:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3卢比可以打去世上任何地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For three rupees you can call anywhere in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.84,0:34:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有个问题 我以为你没有可以求救的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But one thing. I thought you had no one to be calling for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.68,0:34:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个人欠我人情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's one person who owes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.76,0:34:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国际长途\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}ISD.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.68,0:34:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 -拨号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you. -Dial.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.20,0:34:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.95,0:34:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 -嗨 是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah? -Hey. It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.75,0:34:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查理 你在吗 是戴尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Charlie, you there? It's Dale.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.13,0:34:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不该打给我 我们说好了不联络\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You shouldn't be calling me. There's no contact, we said.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.88,0:34:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道...哥们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know. I know, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.59,0:35:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我需要你寄点钱来孟买\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I need you to send me some money to Bombay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.31,0:35:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴尔 欠你的已经还你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dale, you got what you were owed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.89,0:35:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥们 你不能就这样打来继续敲诈我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't just call and expect to keep sucking on the tit, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.86,0:35:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇到大麻烦了 查理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm in serious trouble, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.86,0:35:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对你来说已经习以为常了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's a bit of a habit with you, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.86,0:35:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是四处捅蜂窝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Always got your dick in a vice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.57,0:35:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次与我无关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This one's nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.45,0:35:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你有关 因为你已经毁了我一生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, it is, because my whole life is fucked because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.70,0:35:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 查理 请帮帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, Charlie. Just help me out, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.12,0:35:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你欠我的 -我已经还清了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You owe me. -Not anymore, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.75,0:35:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有 你欠我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, you do. You fucking owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.75,0:35:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是我 你会坐穿牢底\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'd be rotting in a fucking prison cell if it wasn't for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.34,0:35:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.56,0:35:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.31,0:35:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.40,0:36:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.41,0:36:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.58,0:36:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林 等等 -什么 为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lin, wait! -What? What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.67,0:36:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why you trying to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.71,0:36:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你一点也不熟 你对我毫无了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I barely know you. You know nothing about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.59,0:36:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because you're my mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.39,0:36:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 朋友...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, mates. Mates.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.26,0:36:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友只会捅你刀子 相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mates just fuck you over. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.35,0:36:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林 -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lin. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.10,0:36:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 在这里我们一无所有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen. Here, we have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.61,0:36:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果大家不互相扶助 那在这里根本无法活下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This place is not working without everyone helping each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.70,0:36:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林 就像我想帮你一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like I want to help you, Lin.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.58,0:36:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.09,0:37:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一整天都对你态度恶劣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been a total prick to you all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.31,0:37:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.97,0:37:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得出你很不顺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can tell you're having a not-so-good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.56,0:37:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不完全了解自己的处境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Also not fully understanding your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.56,0:37:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在 我认为你已经了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But now, I think you are understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.73,0:37:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 了解我走投无路  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? That I'm totally fucked? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.40,0:37:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在你明白了我们可以开始帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And so now you're understanding we can start getting you...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.53,0:37:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“找路”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"unfuck."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.74,0:37:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“找路” -是的 “找路”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Unfucked." -Yes, "unfuck."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.37,0:37:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With us both working together,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.79,0:37:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能赚得口袋满满 林先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we will make good money fatafat, Linbaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.22,0:37:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那我们快点开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. Then I guess we better get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.97,0:37:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧...老大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chalo. Chalo, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.23,0:37:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这个林是什么样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What kind of man is this Lin, do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.48,0:37:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 但卡拉请他帮忙 他也帮了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know. But Karla asked him for help and he gave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.44,0:38:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接到雷纳尔多咖啡馆的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got a call from Reynaldo's.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.24,0:38:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去过那里 在咖啡馆大闹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was there, making a scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.90,0:38:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道的太多 也不懂得闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He knows more than he should and talks more than I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.96,0:38:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿和平与你相伴 多谢你前来 部长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Assalamu alaikum. Alaikumu assalam. Thank you for coming, Minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.38,0:38:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然的 你召唤 我就来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course. You call, I come.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.84,0:38:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我注意到你有做功课\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have been doing your homework, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.39,0:38:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知识就是力量 鲁祖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Knowledge is power, Rujul.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.10,0:38:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有结合了金钱和影响力时才是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only if you combine with money and influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.06,0:38:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的情况下 还包括一个政府高位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or, in my case, a very fine government position.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.19,0:38:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨嘎尔瓦达的这些人都知道他们完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These people in Sagar Wada all know they are fucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.65,0:38:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是知道这一点并不会给他们赋予力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, there's no power in that for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.57,0:38:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上一次去贫民区是何时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When was the last time you went to one of the jhopadpattis?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.66,0:38:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看那里的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To see the people there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.58,0:38:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚来孟买时曾在其中一个贫民区待过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I first came to Bombay, I spent time in one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.00,0:38:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在早已消失\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's long gone now,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.67,0:39:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我当时所见 现在依然见到的 是那些人不认为自己完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but what I saw then, and still see now, is they do not believe themselves fucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.34,0:39:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们没有头脑 也没有教育以培养野心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They do not have the brains nor the education to foster ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.88,0:39:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有野心的人从不满足于当下 -我们这样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ambitious men are never content. -Men like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.39,0:39:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我的朋友 我们这样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, my friend. Men like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.73,0:39:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你显然已经离开贫民区了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not in the slum any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.31,0:39:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但我一直铭记在那里学到的教训\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, but I never forgot the lessons I learned there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.19,0:39:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠诚高于一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Loyalty is everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.48,0:39:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道瓦利德在周的宫殿学到了什么教训\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wonder what Walid learned at Zhou's palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.41,0:39:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你打算背叛我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you plan to betray me
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.29,0:39:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把萨嘎尔瓦达卖给瓦利德沙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and sell Sagar Wada to Walid Shah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.58,0:39:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是得罪你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have I wronged you in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.71,0:39:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡德尔拜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Khaderbhai--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.71,0:39:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的整个政治生涯都是我赞助的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I financed your entire political career.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.80,0:39:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have been friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.18,0:39:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.68,0:39:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么得罪你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how have I wronged you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.65,0:40:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你落后了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have fallen behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.23,0:40:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你坚持不碰海洛因和性交易生意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your insistence in staying out of the brown sugar and sex trade
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.99,0:40:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意味着你无法和 瓦利德在萨嘎尔瓦达上竞价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}means you cannot compete with Walid's price for Sagar Wada.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.24,0:40:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我没有得罪你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, I did not wrong you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.54,0:40:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就该少赚钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am supposed to make less money
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.04,0:40:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为了你可笑的道德原则\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because of your absurd code of morality?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.46,0:40:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该来找我 我会听你说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you could have come to me. I would've listened.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.18,0:40:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后什么都不做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And done nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.60,0:40:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡达尔 你变得软弱了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have become weak, Khader.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.12,0:41:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.00,0:41:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莎 是塞巴斯蒂安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lisa, it's Sebastian.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.39,0:41:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.01,0:41:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看看你好不好 是否需要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-- I wanted to see if you're okay, if you needed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.27,0:41:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道我在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.56,0:41:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是林 他去雷纳尔多咖啡馆 找毛里齐奥算账\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lin. He came after Maurizio at Reynaldo's.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.90,0:41:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很危险 我认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's dangerous, that one, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.90,0:41:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是林救我出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lin's the one who got me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.48,0:41:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人连我的名字都不清楚 却为了我冒生命危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guy barely knows my name, and he risked his life for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.29,0:41:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛里齐奥知道你来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does Maurizio know you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.25,0:41:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 -他派你来的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. -Did he send you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.88,0:41:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 莉...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Li--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.63,0:41:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莎 我不该让毛里齐奥逼你去那种地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lisa, I shouldn't have let Maurizio make you go to such a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.34,0:41:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该告诉他的 莉莎 我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should've told him. I'm sorry, Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.22,0:42:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻我明白你如何看我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can see how you look at me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.06,0:42:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我应得的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.27,0:42:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懦弱不是你的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not your fault you're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.53,0:42:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I... love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.57,0:42:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 但你照顾不了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. But you can't look after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.08,0:42:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.21,0:42:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你可能需要一些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought you might need some.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.38,0:42:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.71,0:42:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是毛里齐奥让你给我补货 好继续控制我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or did Maurizio tell you to shoot me up so I fall right back into line?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.84,0:42:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 莉莎 毛里齐奥 不知道我来这里 我保证 我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Lisa, Maurizio doesn't know I'm here, I promise. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.22,0:42:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只希望你快乐 仅此而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just want you to be happy. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.60,0:42:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和我 你必须做个选择 莫德纳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Him and me? You're gonna have to choose, Modena.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.98,0:42:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我选你...莉莎 我永远都会选你 永远\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You. You, Lisa. I'd always choose you. Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.28,0:42:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要吗 我可以...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you want this? I-- I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.69,0:42:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想戒毒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I wanna quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.53,0:42:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你爱我 那就帮我戒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You say you love me, then help me with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.20,0:43:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莎 告诉我怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lisa. Just tell me how.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.68,0:43:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是帕拉布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Prabhu.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.55,0:43:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的个人经验 不得不说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From personal experience, I can tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.26,0:43:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么 他都能用最好的价格找到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}anything you want, he can get you at the best prices.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.73,0:43:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是迪特 莎拉和弗朗萨 对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Dieter, Sarah, and Francois. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.60,0:43:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 -很想买上等品质的大麻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. -Keen to buy some top-quality charas.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.32,0:43:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴认识你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.15,0:43:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想要多少大麻  -我们要450克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much charas you are wanting? -We want a pound.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.32,0:43:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量不少啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a lot of smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.49,0:43:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能找到吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.29,0:43:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Arre, of course, this is no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.45,0:43:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们可以去喝啤酒 享受音乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can go drink your beers, enjoy the good music.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.71,0:43:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我送过来 好吗  -不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll bring it, okay? -Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.50,0:43:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 去去就回 -谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. I'll be in in a minute. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.75,0:43:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林先生 我说过吧 这是门好生意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you, Linbaba. Good business.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.34,0:43:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能赚大钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Big money for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.51,0:44:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.93,0:44:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 想观光 买大麻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? You wanna see the sights? Buy some charas?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.52,0:44:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有一千美元 之前麻烦你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a thousand dollars in here for your trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.65,0:44:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有阿穆达巴的一位联络人和一个地址\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and a name and an address in Ahmedabad.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.82,0:44:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方会等你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll be expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.07,0:44:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并给你制作新的护照 钱我出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll make you a new passport at my expense.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.86,0:44:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你需要的 对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what you need, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.28,0:44:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天上午之后发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What changed since this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.66,0:44:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的需要我闭嘴 是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You really need me to keep quiet, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.87,0:44:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林 无论你在找什么 在这里是找不到的 以后不可能了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever you're looking for, Lin, it's not here. Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.05,0:44:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以为找的是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought maybe you were it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.34,0:44:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你知道不是了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now you know different.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.95,0:45:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大麻交易中你那一半的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your half of charas deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.54,0:45:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你留着 我已经得到我需要的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you keep it. I got what I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.13,0:45:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 如果你觉得我是混蛋 我理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I understand if you think I'm a prick,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.25,0:45:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想要一个真正的道别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I would like a proper goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.32,0:45:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会再见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will not be seeing you again, na?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.61,0:45:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.07,0:45:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林先生 你有一颗善良的心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have a good heart, Linbaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.43,0:46:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和卡达尔说了吗  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you tell Khader? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.60,0:46:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们害死了一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then we just got a man killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.77,0:47:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不会困扰你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It doesn't bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.82,0:47:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经做了选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I made my choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.32,0:47:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了你留下的海洛因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I found the heroin you left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.66,0:47:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道我做了什么选择吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wanted to see what choice I'd make?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.37,0:47:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.66,0:47:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林说服我别嗑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lin talked me out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.83,0:47:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让他丢掉毒品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I made him throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.50,0:47:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想改变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanna change.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.42,0:47:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他原本会给你带来好的影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He could've been good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.93,0:47:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚帮他离开孟买了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gave him a way out of Bombay tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.64,0:47:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我能给他最好的东西了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the best thing I could give him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.39,0:47:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺走一条命 拯救一条命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take a life, save a life?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.73,0:47:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就让一切合理了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does that make it all okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.79,0:47:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经我们总是一起跳舞 记得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We danced together all the time, once. Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.21,0:48:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.55,0:48:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那时爱着你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.30,0:48:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要成为你看上去的样子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wanted to be everything you seemed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.18,0:48:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 其实你也知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, then, you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.57,0:48:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.16,0:48:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm leaving. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.95,0:48:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉那个疯女人周我要走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You tell that mad cow Zhou I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.50,0:48:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要离开孟买 不需要这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm leaving Bombay. There's no need for any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.75,0:48:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.38,0:48:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.13,0:50:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次我真的想吸取教训\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was trying to learn my lesson for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.76,0:50:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学着聪明点 做我需要做的 为了存活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be smart and do what I needed to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.55,0:50:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了自由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.21,0:50:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(改编自格里高利大卫罗伯茨的 小说《Shantaram》)
